PN,41101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,FPolice in Northern Ireland have urged
OL,8,Fanyone with information about claims
OL,9,Fthat officers advised nurses to show
OL,10,FID to masked men during disorder last
OL,11,Fweek to report it.
OL,13,FIt comes after Stormont First Minister
OL,14,FMichelle O'Neill called on police to
OL,15,Fget to the bottom of the claims and
OL,16,Fcontacted PSNI Chief Constable Jon
OL,17,FBoutcher about the allegations.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,FPolice said on Monday evening that no-
OL,8,Fone had made direct contact making
OL,9,Fsuch allegations, but said they were
OL,10,Fengaging with healthcare worker
OL,11,Frepresentatives.
OL,13,FThe claims first emerged last week
OL,14,Famid the violence that erupted in
OL,15,Fparts of the city after a knife attack
OL,16,Fin north Belfast in which Stephen
OL,17,FOgilvie, who is aged in his 40s, lost
OL,18,Fan eye.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,FSudanese national Hadi Alodid, 30,
OL,8,Fappeared at Belfast Magistrates' Court
OL,9,Fon Wednesday, charged with attempted
OL,10,Fmurder over the incident.
OL,12,FAnti-immigration disorder that broke
OL,13,Fout in response to the stabbing saw
OL,14,Fmobs set homes, a bus and cars on fire
OL,15,F` with people targeted based on their
OL,16,Frace.
OL,18,FMs O'Neill said the suggestion that
OL,19,Fmasked gangs were asking nurses to
OL,20,Fshow their ID as they travelled to
OL,21,Fwork was "vile and disgusting".
OL,26,@}D@JOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,FShe expressed particular concern about
OL,8,Fa claim that police officers close to
OL,9,Fthe Mater Hospital in north Belfast
OL,10,Fhad advised healthcare staff to show
OL,11,Ftheir IDs to the rioters as they
OL,12,Fpassed "checkpoints" set up by the
OL,13,Fgangs.
OL,15,F"It's absolutely vile and disgusting,"
OL,16,Fsaid Ms O'Neill.
OL,26,@tD@HOUtD@TO]wD@AOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,F"I've raised it directly with the
OL,8,FChief Constable. I know that our team
OL,9,Fin the Policing Board (PSNI oversight
OL,10,Fbody) also raised this issue, and I've
OL,11,Fasked the Chief Constable to do a full
OL,12,Finvestigation into this, because I've
OL,13,Fbeen told by members who work in one
OL,14,Fof our local hospitals that they stood
OL,15,Fwith police and were told to show
OL,16,Ftheir ID to masked men on the street.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,F"If that happened, there needs to be a
OL,8,Fserious investigation. No nurse or no
OL,9,Fperson going into the workplace to
OL,10,Fstop at any mob and give their ID.
OL,11,FThat's absolutely disgraceful."
OL,13,FShe added: "I think we have to get to
OL,14,Fthe bottom of whether or not that did
OL,15,Fhappen. I put it directly to the Chief
OL,16,FConstable, who, in the first instance,
OL,17,Fdismissed it, but then, whenever I
OL,18,Fwent back to him again, he had to take
OL,19,Fon board that actually both myself and
OL,20,Fthe Health Minister (Mike Nesbitt)
OL,21,Fwere told this by members of staff."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@_O]uD@LOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,FAssistant Chief Constable Ryan
OL,8,FHenderson said police received reports
OL,9,Fof vehicles being stopped by masked
OL,10,Fgangs in the Greater Belfast area.
OL,12,F"Officers responded immediately and a
OL,13,Fsignificant mobile policing presence
OL,14,Fwas maintained for a period of time to
OL,15,Fprovide reassurance and prevent the
OL,16,Fcommission of offences," he said in a
OL,17,Fstatement on Monday evening.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,F"We are aware of reports circulating
OL,8,Fthat police officers may have advised
OL,9,Fnursing staff outside the Mater
OL,10,FHospital to show their ID to masked
OL,11,Fmen.
OL,13,F"We are checking our records of
OL,14,FTuesday evening to establish if we can
OL,15,Fidentify any specific reports.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,F"I have also engaged directly with the
OL,8,FChief Executive of the Belfast Trust
OL,9,Fand with senior staff at the Mater
OL,10,FHospital in order to obtain any
OL,11,Fspecific examples they might be aware
OL,12,Fof.
OL,14,F"No one has come to police directly at
OL,15,Fthis stage and we would urge anyone
OL,16,Fwho experienced this or who has
OL,17,Finformation to contact us on 101."
OL,19,FThe Royal College of Nursing engaged
OL,20,Fwith the PSNI on the issue last week.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,FWhile the race-related violence has
OL,8,Fdied down since Tuesday and Wednesday
OL,9,Fof last week, the weekend did see some
OL,10,Fisolated incidents in parts of Belfast
OL,11,Fand beyond.
OL,13,FTwo men were arrested after criminal
OL,14,Fdamage was caused to a property and
OL,15,Fvehicle in the Donegall Avenue area of
OL,16,Fsouth Belfast, while a house in north
OL,17,FBelfast was targeted in an arson
OL,18,Fattack.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,FA Together Against Hate rally took
OL,8,Fplace outside Belfast City Hall on
OL,9,FSaturday afternoon, with an estimated
OL,10,F3,000 demonstrators in attendance.
OL,12,FThe PSNI has been approached for
OL,13,Fcomment on Ms O'Neill's remarks.
OL,15,FLater, Health Minister Mike Nesbitt
OL,16,Fwas asked directly about "checkpoints"
OL,17,Fat the Mater Hospital and police
OL,18,Fallegedly advising workers to show
OL,19,Fthem their ID by SDLP MLA Colin
OL,20,FMcGrath during an urgent oral question.
OL,26,@xD@ZOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,FMr Nesbitt responded by saying he had
OL,8,Fbeen in the Mater last week and "heard
OL,9,Fa number of quite horrendous stories
OL,10,Fwhich I will not share with the House
OL,11,Fbecause some of those stories would
OL,12,Fidentify specific nurses and put them
OL,13,Fback at risk".
OL,26,@pD@aOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,F"I did hear of one young nurse who had
OL,8,Fto negotiate her own way through the
OL,9,Frioters, through the barricades down
OL,10,Fat Carlisle Circus, that's not right,
OL,11,Fand that's one of the conversations
OL,12,Fthat I had with the Chief Constable
OL,13,Fand I will assure the Member Mr
OL,14,FBoutcher took that very seriously
OL,15,Findeed," he told MLAs.
OL,17,FMr Nesbitt also said the "appalling
OL,18,Fevents" of last week have "left a mark
OL,19,Fon healthcare staff, particularly our
OL,20,Finternational colleagues, some of whom
OL,21,Fhave endured horrendous experiences".
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@HO]yD@ZOUzD@GO]zD@[OU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,F"Many of the issues faced by staff
OL,8,Fgaining access over the past week have
OL,9,Fbeen in relation to disturbances in
OL,10,Fsurrounding areas rather than on the
OL,11,Fcampus itself," he said.
OL,13,F"The safety of staff is paramount and
OL,14,Fa range of security measures are in
OL,15,Fplace, dedicated security teams are
OL,16,Favailable 24 hours a day across our
OL,17,Fmain sites.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@OO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,F"They're trained in prevention and
OL,8,Fmanagement of violence and aggression.
OL,9,FThey carry out regular patrols, they
OL,10,Fmonitor CCTV and they liaise with the
OL,11,FPSNI.
OL,13,F"The disturbances have largely centred
OL,14,Fon the Belfast area, particularly the
OL,15,FMater. The Belfast Trust engage
OL,16,Fregularly with the PSNI, including a
OL,17,Fmeeting with the deputy chief
OL,18,Fconstable on June 11.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781553961
OL,3,CPolice engaging with nurses over
OL,4,Cclaims officers told them to show
OL,5,Cmasked men ID
OL,7,F"This resulted in an observable
OL,8,Fincrease in police presence, both in
OL,9,Fthe vicinity of the Mater and also on
OL,10,Fsite and within the emergency
OL,11,Fdepartment with police liaising with
OL,12,Fstaff on the ground.
OL,14,F"Trust security staff and duty
OL,15,Fmanagers also provide a range of
OL,16,Finterventions to support staff that
OL,17,Fwill be deployed going forward when
OL,18,Frequired."
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@JO]
